inks ==\n*{{Cycling Archives|2510}}\n*[http://histo.letour.fr/HISTO/us/TDF/coureur/2093.html Official Tour de France results for Ottavio Bottecchia]\n\n{{Tour de France general classification winners}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bottecchia, Ottavio}}\n[[Category:1894 births]]\n[[Category:1927 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from the Province of Treviso]]\n[[Category:Italian male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Tour de France winners]]\n[[Category:Murdered sportspeople]]\n[[Category:Unsolved murders in Italy]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Veneto]]\n[[Category:Tour de France cyclists]]\n", "name_user": "Lepricavark", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:added short description", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ottavio_Bottecchia"}
